take one apple from the countertop
take the apple and move to reach the microwave oven
then place the apple in the microwave oven

then place the apple in the fridge

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the microwave and turn right, head to the counter top.
Pick up the apple from the counter top.
Turn right and walk, then turn left and head to the microwave.
Put the apple into the microwave, heat it up, and pick it up back.
Turn left and walk across the counter top then turn left and walk towards the fridge.
Put the apple beside the another apple in the last rack of the fridge.

high_descs: Move forward, turn right, walk straight, take right towards the counter top.
Take the apple from the counter top.
Turn right, move towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, close it, turn on, wait, turn off, open the microwave, get back the apple, close the microwave.
Take left, walk straight, turn left towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the apple inside bottom rack in the fridge, close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To take apple from the counter top, heat it, put it in the fridge.
